text_copy.text:
#ThisIsARunnersBody

 

We all have insecurities about our bodies. Whether it’s comparing ourselves to an ideal or trying to live up to expectations; when it comes to running, most of us are full of insecurities.

Altra, along with renowned athlete Kara Goucher, want to change to conversation around how we feel about our bodies and running. A runner’s body is strong. A runner’s body is capable of overcoming obstacles. Our bodies are worthy of love and when we run, we express that love. Join us and Kara by sharing your story about struggles you’ve experienced related to loving your body using the hashtag #ThisIsARunnersBody.

 

03-08-2022
